  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. All 13 credibility factors are assessed. Decision: Accepted. NOTE (adversarial): the bound claim is richly described and appears well-supported by the validation results, but the Claim node itself carries no prov:wasDerivedFrom link to any Evidence — it is an orphan claim (W-EP-01).",
