      "description": "Grid convergence index (GCI) study across three mesh refinement levels (coarse 2.1M, medium 5.8M, fine 14.2M cells). GCI for NIH at the finest-to-medium ratio is 1.8%, below the 5% acceptability criterion for MRL 5.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/mesh-gci-study-report-cou2",
